Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.15,0:00:05.30,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,I have to leave for dress rehearsal soon, Rarity!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.30,0:00:06.56,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,Is it finished yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.10,0:00:08.38,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Not quite.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.38,0:00:11.57,Rarity,,0,0,0,,I still feel it needs a certain je ne sais quoi.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.57,0:00:12.93,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Perhaps its needs…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.93,0:00:14.27,Rarity,,0,0,0,,appliqués
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.27,0:00:15.35,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,Appliqués?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.30,0:00:17.01,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Or…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.01,0:00:18.14,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Sequins
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.14,0:00:19.05,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,Sequins!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.87,0:00:25.10,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Sweetie Belle,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.10,0:00:28.14,Rarity,,0,0,0,,I adore having you help me, truly I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.14,0:00:29.34,Rarity,,0,0,0,,But…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.62,0:00:31.92,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,Guess I got a little carried away.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.92,0:00:34.22,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,It's just that I know how important it is for you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.22,0:00:37.78,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,to finish this wardrobe in time for Sapphire Shores and her backup dancers.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.78,0:00:40.98,Rarity,,0,0,0,,This is without a doubt my most prestigious order ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.98,0:00:44.43,Rarity,,0,0,0,,After all, Sapphire Shores is the pony of pop.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.43,0:00:47.81,Rarity,,0,0,0,,And her Equestria-wide tour launches in Canterlot next week.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.81,0:00:51.67,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Which means she must have these outfits by day after tomorrow at the latest!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.67,0:00:52.78,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,But is there time?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.78,0:00:53.73,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Barely.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.73,0:00:55.63,Rarity,,0,0,0,,But I work well under pressure.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.22,0:00:58.60,Rarity,,0,0,0,,As long as I stay calm, I'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.60,0:00:59.39,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.39,0:00:59.94,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.94,0:01:00.54,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,Then…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.54,0:01:03.98,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,maybe you could check this stitching and finish the buttons on the dresses
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.98,0:01:06.46,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,that I made for me, Applebloom and Scootaloo?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.46,0:01:09.18,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,I really want them to look perfect, and…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.18,0:01:12.22,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,I think I need your expertise.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.22,0:01:14.58,Rarity,,0,0,0,,My, you've been so much help to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.58,0:01:16.75,Rarity,,0,0,0,,How I could possibly say "No"?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.75,0:01:18.05,Rarity,,0,0,0,,When do you need them?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.05,0:01:19.08,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow night.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.08,0:01:21.08,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,For the opening night of our show!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.95,0:01:26.55,Rarity,,0,0,0,,But Sweetie Belle, darling, I'm behind as it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.53,0:01:29.02,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.49,0:01:32.15,Rarity,,0,0,0,,I suppose…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.15,0:01:36.00,Rarity,,0,0,0,,if I got a few more ponies to help me, then maybe…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.00,0:01:37.85,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,Oh thank you, thank you, thank you, thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.85,0:01:39.54,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,You're the best sister ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.54,0:01:41.19,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,The dresses are right over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.77,0:02:26.11,Cheerilee,,0,0,0,,My goodness, girls!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.11,0:02:27.19,Cheerilee,,0,0,0,,It's time!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.19,0:02:29.17,Cheerilee,,0,0,0,,And the audience is almost fully seated!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.17,0:02:30.50,Cheerilee,,0,0,0,,Costumes!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.36,0:02:34.64,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,I can't believe Rarity still isn't here with the costumes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.64,0:02:36.55,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,She's been very busy lately!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.55,0:02:38.75,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,But how can she still not be here?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.75,0:02:40.86,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,She's known about this for weeks!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.04,0:02:46.03,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,She has known about this for weeks, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.42,0:02:49.83,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,I kept meaning to ask her, I really did, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.83,0:02:51.63,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,I worked so hard on this play,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.63,0:02:53.65,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,I wrote it especially for the three of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.65,0:02:56.61,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,I directed it, I'm in it, I made the costumes…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.61,0:03:01.10,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,It's just that this is really my time to shine doing something completely myself,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.10,0:03:03.64,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,and I really wanted to keep it that way!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.64,0:03:05.91,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,But we wanted everything to be perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.91,0:03:08.23,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,All our friends came out to see it tonight!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.23,0:03:09.95,Cheerilee,,0,0,0,,Places!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.51,0:03:14.48,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm here, I'm here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.08,0:03:16.19,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,You made it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.19,0:03:19.00,Rarity,,0,0,0,,I beg your pardon for cutting it so close,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.00,0:03:21.69,Rarity,,0,0,0,,but I made some improvements to your original design,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.69,0:03:25.27,Rarity,,0,0,0,,and I had a terrible time with these froofy sleeves.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.27,0:03:27.65,Rarity,,0,0,0,,It is for the first play you ever wrote, after all,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.65,0:03:30.22,Rarity,,0,0,0,,so I made quite certain it came out just so.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.22,0:03:31.27,Cheerilee,,0,0,0,,Places!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.27,0:03:32.66,Cheerilee,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.96,0:03:55.79,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Forsooth and anon,{\i0} \N {\i1}I cometh forthwith{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.79,0:03:59.92,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and posthaste{\i0} \N {\i1}with glad tidings, miladies.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.38,0:04:02.24,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.24,0:04:04.11,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,A standing ovation!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.11,0:04:06.47,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,I still have goosebumps!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.47,0:04:09.59,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,This must be like a dream come true for you, huh, Sweetie Belle?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.59,0:04:13.07,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,Ooh, can you imagine if this show was how you got your cutie mark?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.07,0:04:14.55,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Which do you think you'd get it for?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.55,0:04:17.08,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Writing, directing, or acting?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.44,0:04:21.31,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,Let's not get carried away.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.31,0:04:25.60,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,We've got a whole lobby full of friends waiting to shower us with adoration and praise.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.60,0:04:27.69,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,Try to be gracious.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.69,0:04:29.24,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,Modest.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.24,0:04:30.47,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Classy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.61,0:04:38.44,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,Here we are! The stars of the show!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.51,0:04:41.99,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,You may tell us how much you loved it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.99,0:04:43.34,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,Line forms here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.34,0:04:44.47,Spike,,0,0,0,,Wow, you guys,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.47,0:04:46.33,Spike,,0,0,0,,I think your sisters would've loved it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.33,0:04:47.67,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Would have?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.67,0:04:51.39,Spike,,0,0,0,,They're sorry, but they had to go help Rarity get Saphire Shores's wardrobe ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.39,0:04:52.98,Spike,,0,0,0,,to take to Canterlot in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.98,0:04:54.77,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,Even Rainbow Dash?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.77,0:04:55.76,Spike,,0,0,0,,Yeah…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.76,0:04:58.50,Spike,,0,0,0,,Rarity fell {\i1}way{\i0} behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.08,0:05:02.41,Spike,,0,0,0,,Aw, cheer up, the show was great!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.41,0:05:04.03,Spike,,0,0,0,,I'll get you some punch.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.03,0:05:07.12,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,At least everypony else who was able to stay loved it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.99,0:05:13.52,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,What did you all like best? The writing, the directing, or the acting?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.21,0:05:17.71,Lemon Hearts,,0,0,0,,Oh my, I- I loved the dresses.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.71,0:05:20.23,Noteworthy,,0,0,0,,I liked some of those lines you said.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.23,0:05:22.01,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,Oh really? Which ones?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.01,0:05:24.13,Noteworthy,,0,0,0,,Ah, I don't really remember,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.13,0:05:28.37,Noteworthy,,0,0,0,,but you were wearing a pink taffeta dress with lots of chiffone when you said them!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.37,0:05:31.14,Noteworthy,,0,0,0,,Whoo-ee, that outfit was a dazzler!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.14,0:05:36.03,Lemon Hearts,,0,0,0,,I liked that one almost as much as the one with the lace trim and all the embroidered cuffs!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.03,0:05:38.13,Noteworthy,,0,0,0,,That was a nice one too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.37,0:05:44.22,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,Isn't there anypony here who remembers anything about the play besides the dresses?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.35,0:05:58.56,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,All of this is one headpiece?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.56,0:05:59.65,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.13,0:06:04.44,Rarity,,0,0,0,,This marvelous extravagance is the créme de la créme of the entire wardrobe!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.13,0:06:09.42,Rarity,,0,0,0,,But alas, without this key hidden stitch, it's just a…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.29,0:06:13.95,Rarity,,0,0,0,,I'm trying to think of a nicer way to say 'big bummer'.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.49,0:06:21.88,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Now perhaps we can all at last take a moment to relax!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.53,0:06:26.32,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Whatever's the matter, Sweetie Belle?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.32,0:06:28.23,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Didn't the play go all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.23,0:06:29.66,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,Not even close.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.66,0:06:32.93,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Oh dear. Was something amiss with the dresses I made you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.93,0:06:36.24,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,No, they were perfect, and that was the whole problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.79,0:06:44.50,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Oh, um, I think maybe we'll go take that moment to relax now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.50,0:06:47.13,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Heh, sure do feel like relaxing!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.13,0:06:48.59,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Right behind ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.18,0:06:52.85,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,How could you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.80,0:06:55.71,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,"Oh, what amazing dresses!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.71,0:06:57.56,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,Oh, how I love the dresses!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.56,0:07:00.38,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,Ooh, dresses, dresses, dresses, dresses!"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.71,0:07:03.72,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Oh, so they did like them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.27,0:07:06.42,Rarity,,0,0,0,,You had me worried, you silly filly.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.42,0:07:09.67,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,There! I knew it! You did this on purpose!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.67,0:07:15.00,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,Stealing the spotlight like you always do! It's my fifth birthday party all over again!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.00,0:07:16.37,Rarity,,0,0,0,,The… the what now?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.37,0:07:18.05,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,Don't act like you don't remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.05,0:07:21.15,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,Or are you trying to prove you're a better actress than me too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.15,0:07:23.76,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Sweetie Belle, if I did anything to upset you, then--
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.76,0:07:26.51,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,Admit you made those dresses too good on purpose!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.51,0:07:28.09,Rarity,,0,0,0,,I thought they were supposed to be good.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.09,0:07:31.36,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,Yes, good. Not jaw-dropping amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.36,0:07:33.65,Rarity,,0,0,0,,I only tried to do what I thought you wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.65,0:07:34.50,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,Ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.82,0:07:43.55,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,I don't believe it. After everything I put up with all week long!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.55,0:07:46.28,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,"Sweetie Belle, get me some red ribbon!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.28,0:07:48.79,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,No, that's not red, that's cherry!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.79,0:07:50.95,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,No, that's not red, that's cinnamon!"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.95,0:07:53.10,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,For Pete's sake, it's all red!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.10,0:07:55.24,Rarity,,0,0,0,,I should probably go talk to her, hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.24,0:07:58.80,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,At least Sapphire Shores won't be all like "Ooh, who fetched you that red ribbon?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.80,0:08:00.91,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,Because I don't care about anything else you made,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.91,0:08:03.53,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,all I care about is that amazing red ribbon!"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.53,0:08:05.53,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Perhaps waiting would be best.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.87,0:08:23.33,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,Now I can't even sleep! Happy now, big sis?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.20,0:08:31.67,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,I wish there was a way I could take back all the work I did!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.88,0:08:46.24,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,Even better.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.02,0:09:09.34,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,Now what?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.98,0:09:20.20,Somepony,,0,0,0,,And the winner of the best writer director actor in an awesome play
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.20,0:09:23.91,Somepony,,0,0,0,,put on by a pony and her awesome best friends goes to…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.91,0:09:25.92,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Sweetie Belle!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.25,0:09:43.89,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,Don't go!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.32,0:09:56.87,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,Stop! Why do you have to ruin everything?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.88,0:10:02.08,Luna,,0,0,0,,Enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.06,0:10:12.17,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,Princess Luna! It's really you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.17,0:10:13.56,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,Or am I dreaming?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.56,0:10:15.54,Luna,,0,0,0,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.54,0:10:16.48,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,Let me see…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.48,0:10:19.98,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,You just rescued me from an maniacal laughing Rarity cloud.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.98,0:10:21.76,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'm probably dreaming.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.76,0:10:24.85,Luna,,0,0,0,,I understand what you are going through, Sweetie Belle.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.85,0:10:28.42,Luna,,0,0,0,,I too have a sister who often shines more brightly than me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.42,0:10:31.03,Luna,,0,0,0,,And with this… I have struggled.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.09,0:10:36.51,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,Wait! Come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.51,0:10:38.59,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,Luna! Can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.59,0:10:40.71,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,Thank you for what you did!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.33,0:10:43.16,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,Help! Luna!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.16,0:10:45.85,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,Luna-a-a-a!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.96,0:10:55.13,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,I remember this. This is my fifth birthday party.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.61,0:10:59.57,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,I decided to make a grand entrance.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.57,0:11:02.67,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,I made myself all beautiful. Just like my big sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.16,0:11:05.84,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,Finally… I was perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.84,0:11:09.20,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,And then went to the stairs to enter like the belle of the ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.20,0:11:13.65,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,When I finally came out of my room, I found the party going out without me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.65,0:11:19.43,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,And I kept posing at the top of the stairs waiting to be noticed, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.43,0:11:20.69,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,All I heard was…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.69,0:11:23.53,Somepony,,0,0,0,,This party favors are the coolest!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.18,0:11:27.37,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Awesome! Where did you get these?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.37,0:11:30.96,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Made them myself. And of course you'll all want cake. Won't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.21,0:11:34.14,Somepony,,0,0,0,,You are the greatest, Rarity!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.14,0:11:39.19,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Who needs a birthday girl when you've got a birthday girl's amazing big sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.51,0:11:48.24,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,That's when I learned never try to shine with my big sister around.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.24,0:11:51.16,Luna,,0,0,0,,But perhaps you didn't have the whole story.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.16,0:11:53.41,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,I thought that you said you understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.41,0:11:54.15,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,Luna?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.18,0:11:58.90,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Where is Sweetie Belle?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.72,0:12:02.11,Rarity,,0,0,0,,I'm sure she will be along in any moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.13,0:12:05.09,Somepony,,0,0,0,,I'm tired of waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.09,0:12:08.92,Somepony,,0,0,0,,I say we get out of here before we all keel over from boredom.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.92,0:12:10.09,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Who is with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.19,0:12:14.19,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Poor Sweetie Belle.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.19,0:12:18.50,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Nopony is gonna come to another one of her parties after this fiasco.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.25,0:12:21.72,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Don't go! You'll miss one of the…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.72,0:12:23.05,Rarity,,0,0,0,,party favors.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.89,0:12:27.13,Rarity,,0,0,0,,I was going to save it to the end, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.07,0:12:32.89,Somepony,,0,0,0,,These party favors are the coolest!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.57,0:12:36.69,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Awesome! Where did you get these?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.69,0:12:40.06,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Made them myself. And of course you'll all want cake. Won't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.67,0:12:46.59,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Who needs a birthday girl when you've got a birthday girl's amazing big sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.48,0:12:52.93,Rarity,,0,0,0,,All of these things were Sweetie Belle's idea
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.93,0:12:55.52,Rarity,,0,0,0,,I just assisted with the execution.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.74,0:12:58.83,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,I guess Rarity wasn't trying to steal the spotlight.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.83,0:13:00.96,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,She was trying to save my party.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.08,0:13:03.02,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,Luna?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.26,0:13:11.18,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,Luna!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.99,0:13:36.52,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Should I hem the cloaks now or wait until I'm there?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.52,0:13:39.50,Rarity,,0,0,0,,I could hand them now, but… I might have to redo them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.50,0:13:40.67,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,When was this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.67,0:13:45.47,Rarity,,0,0,0,,What if I wait until I'm in Canterlot to hand them?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.47,0:13:46.41,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.41,0:13:48.77,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,This must have happen earlier tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.87,0:13:53.85,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Sapphire Shores is such a big star and such a stickler for details.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.85,0:13:55.77,Rarity,,0,0,0,,What if everything is not perfect enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.34,0:14:00.11,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,Funny. I thought i was the only one who got worried about stuff like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.38,0:14:03.11,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Buck up, Rarity! Stop this foolishness.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.11,0:14:05.21,Rarity,,0,0,0,,You've done your best and left nothing to chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.21,0:14:08.15,Rarity,,0,0,0,,All that's needed now is… good night's rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.62,0:14:14.40,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,I hope everything goes allright for her tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.05,0:14:17.40,Luna,,0,0,0,,How curious you should say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.74,0:14:19.67,Luna,,0,0,0,,Go.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.67,0:14:24.11,Luna,,0,0,0,,Go see what the future holds if you fail to rein in your worst instincts.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.11,0:14:25.77,Luna,,0,0,0,,As I once did.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.53,0:14:35.37,Rarity,,0,0,0,,And here it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.37,0:14:36.91,Rarity,,0,0,0,,The crème de la crème.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.91,0:14:37.95,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.95,0:14:39.80,Rarity,,0,0,0,,The pièce de résistance.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.80,0:14:40.75,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.76,0:14:50.71,Rarity,,0,0,0,,The headdress!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.80,0:14:55.03,SapphireShores,,0,0,0,,Looks like I made a mistake here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.61,0:15:00.38,Rarity,,0,0,0,,B… But, but this is impossible. I… I checked and re-checked everything. This couldn't have happened!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.38,0:15:01.88,SapphireShores,,0,0,0,,You sure about that, honey?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.97,0:15:04.30,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Please. You must believe me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.37,0:15:06.42,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,Listen to my sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.61,0:15:23.93,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,I don't want to see anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.93,0:15:25.53,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Always check and re-check.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.53,0:15:31.24,SapphireShores,,0,0,0,,Who wants to hear a funny story about my ex-costume designer?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.61,0:15:34.72,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Check! Re-check! Re-check and re-check!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.72,0:15:38.85,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,Make it stop! Princess Luna can you hear me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.85,0:15:41.75,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Make me a dress, Rarity. Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.75,0:15:42.85,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Go away!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.85,0:15:45.62,Rarity,,0,0,0,,You know I don't do that anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.90,0:15:52.94,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,Wake me up, Princess Luna, wake me up, wake me up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.80,0:16:01.35,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,Rarity?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.35,0:16:04.76,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,Oh no! The box is… gone…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.76,0:16:06.23,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,I'm too late!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.23,0:16:09.35,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,She left for Canterlot!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.07,0:16:20.31,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,The key is for you two to distract Rarity long enough for me to put the stitch back in without her noticing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.79,0:16:22.89,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,If we're not too late already.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.89,0:16:26.21,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Oh my gosh! I can't believe we're going to see Sapphire Shores!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.21,0:16:27.50,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,I'm such a huge fan!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.50,0:16:28.84,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,I know all her songs!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.84,0:16:30.81,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,"Get Your Pony On"!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.81,0:16:32.33,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,That's one of my favorites!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.33,0:16:34.97,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,This isn't a trip to see Sapphire Shores!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.97,0:16:37.81,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,It's a trip to save my sister from a horrible future!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.81,0:16:39.78,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,"Serves Her Right"!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.78,0:16:41.53,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,How can you say that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.53,0:16:43.44,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,Rarity doesn't deserve it at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.44,0:16:47.50,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,No! "Serves Her Right" as another one of Sapphire Shores's songs!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.50,0:16:49.16,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,You seriously didn't know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.16,0:16:51.59,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Don't you listen to her music?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.59,0:16:54.09,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,I prefer show tunes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.86,0:16:59.54,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Five, six, seven and ba-bam!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.54,0:17:04.26,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Oh, bravo! Fabulous! Magnifique!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.26,0:17:06.79,SapphireShores,,0,0,0,,One more time. From the top.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.79,0:17:10.96,SapphireShores,,0,0,0,,Let's not embarras me in front of my favorite designer this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.96,0:17:13.99,SapphireShores,,0,0,0,,And one, two, three, four.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.65,0:17:16.84,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,But you have to let us in!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.84,0:17:19.89,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,I'm Sapphire Shores' designer's sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.81,0:17:22.71,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,You have to believe us!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.71,0:17:30.60,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Kid. The only thing I have to do is make sure Sapphire Shores doesn't get interrupted all day by fans like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.60,0:17:32.11,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,But I'm not a fan!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.11,0:17:32.94,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.94,0:17:34.04,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,Me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.04,0:17:35.49,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,Not helping!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.56,0:17:42.00,SapphireShores,,0,0,0,,Now that's how I like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.00,0:17:43.86,SapphireShores,,0,0,0,,You rocked it, girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.86,0:17:46.58,SapphireShores,,0,0,0,,Get some water and be back in ten.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.95,0:17:50.63,SapphireShores,,0,0,0,,Rarity, come on up here and show me what you brought me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.63,0:17:53.83,SapphireShores,,0,0,0,,Sapphire wants to see it and love it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.73,0:17:58.84,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,Almost…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.62,0:18:03.39,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,We've got to get in there, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.22,0:18:13.00,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,Okay then. Liking what I see so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.00,0:18:15.24,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,So, is this the whole shebang?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.24,0:18:18.45,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Actually, I saved the best for last.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.04,0:18:32.52,Rarity,,0,0,0,,And here it is…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.86,0:18:36.81,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,You've got to see this with the cinnamon ribbon.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.81,0:18:37.76,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,You'll love it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.76,0:18:39.24,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Sweetie Belle!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.24,0:18:41.24,SapphireShores,,0,0,0,,You know her?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.79,0:18:44.43,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Just a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.09,0:19:13.78,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,Oh, good. This is just a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.78,0:19:16.76,Luna,,0,0,0,,Actually no. This is very much real.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.66,0:19:21.26,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,Oh Luna. I wish none of this ever happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.26,0:19:22.89,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,What am I gonna do?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.89,0:19:25.53,Luna,,0,0,0,,Let's begin with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.32,0:19:30.62,Luna,,0,0,0,,And I think I know how you can even improve it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.67,0:19:38.31,Rarity,,0,0,0,,I would like to know what in a wide wide realm of Equestria this stunt of yours is all about.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.31,0:19:40.62,Rarity,,0,0,0,,And I want to know now!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.62,0:19:45.00,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Do you have any idea how important this job is to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.00,0:19:47.10,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,Actually I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.10,0:19:50.39,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,I was upset at you for stealing spotlight from me at the play,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.39,0:19:53.88,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,so I pulled out the center stitch to the head piece so it would fall apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.88,0:19:55.25,Rarity,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.25,0:19:58.78,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,But then I realized I didn't want your future to be ruined forever and ever,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.78,0:20:01.97,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,so I came back to change it before it was too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.97,0:20:05.10,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,So… here it is. It's all fixed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.10,0:20:07.86,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,Please forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.86,0:20:11.13,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Wait… What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.13,0:20:11.98,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,Trust me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.98,0:20:14.63,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,Sapphire Shores is gonna love it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.26,0:20:20.73,SapphireShores,,0,0,0,,Rarity, this isn't going to work out.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.73,0:20:24.60,SapphireShores,,0,0,0,,You don't get to my level of success without learning to read the signs.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.60,0:20:28.20,SapphireShores,,0,0,0,,And this situation has bad luck written all over it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.20,0:20:32.46,Rarity,,0,0,0,,I promise you'll absolutely adore the headdress as soon as you see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.59,0:20:45.32,SapphireShores,,0,0,0,,My! It is attractive, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.32,0:20:48.47,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,Look at the stitching. Real close.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.59,0:20:53.81,SapphireShores,,0,0,0,,Well, I'll bet. It's a dolphin!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.81,0:20:55.77,SapphireShores,,0,0,0,,That's my lucky animal!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.77,0:20:58.49,SapphireShores,,0,0,0,,They swum with me in my dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.49,0:21:01.98,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Wherever did you come up with the idea for a dolphin?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.98,0:21:06.63,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,Oh, it just came to me. In a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.02,0:21:12.79,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry I got jealous about those dresses.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.79,0:21:15.11,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,I know now that you were only trying to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.11,0:21:18.02,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Oh, Sweetie, I forgive you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.02,0:21:20.30,Rarity,,0,0,0,,But I never did get to see your play.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.30,0:21:23.54,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Any chance I can catch an encore performance?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.54,0:21:26.15,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,I don't think the play was all that good.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.15,0:21:30.22,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,To be honest, the costumes were the best part.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.07,0:21:35.51,Somepony,,0,0,0,,СЧАСТЛИВЫЙ ПОНЕЦ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.51,0:21:38.27,Somepony,,0,0,0,,anon2anon \Nsunnysubs.com
